Intelligent Tutoring System extension

* The extension is only available for NUS(National University of Singapore) students.

The extension aims to enhance your Java learning experience on Coursemology - an assignment submission platform, with the ITS(Intelligent Tutoring System) extension. The extension will read student Java program and generate repair suggestions and learning points for student to have better understanding of the data structures and algorithms.

Key Features:

Minimum set-up required: Require a one-time activation and you can generate feedback by simply navigating to the Coursemology edit page.

Deepen Understanding: Our extension provides explanations and tips, to help you have a better understanding of data structures, algorithms and code practices.
